Combine mustard and mayonnaise in a small bowl. Spread on bread slices. Place 2 slices ham on one slice of bread. Top with Swiss cheese, remaining 2 slices ham, American cheese, pickle slices, and remaining bread slice. Place sandwich on hot grill or skillet. Press down on sandwich with a spatula while toasting and cook for 3 to 5 minutes, or until cheeses are melted and sandwich is hot, turning sandwich over once.